现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Robbie-Williams-and-The-Beatles.-Credit-Leo-Baron-and-Ted-West-via-Getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="罗比·威廉姆斯和甲壳虫乐队。学分：狮子座男爵和泰德·韦斯特（通过盖蒂）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Robbie-Williams-and-The-Beatles.-Credit-Leo-Baron-and-Ted-West-via-Getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Robbie-Williams-and-The-Beatles.-Credit-Leo-Baron-and-Ted-West-via-Getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Robbie-Williams-and-The-Beatles.-Credit-Leo-Baron-and-Ted-West-via-Getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Robbie-Williams-and-The-Beatles.-Credit-Leo-Baron-and-Ted-West-via-Getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Robbie-Williams-and-The-Beatles.-Credit-Leo-Baron-and-Ted-West-via-Getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Robbie-Williams-and-The-Beatles.-Credit-Leo-Baron-and-Ted-West-via-Getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Robbie-Williams">罗比·威廉姆斯（Robbie Williams）</a>与<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/better-man-review-robbie-williams-strangest-music-biopic-3807590"><em>“更好的人”</em></a>配乐获得了他的第15张专辑，这使他与<a href="/artists/The-Beatles">甲壳虫乐队</a>捆绑在一起。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-interviews/robbie-williams-director-michael-gracey-biopic-better-man-interview-3821636">罗比·威廉姆斯（Robbie Williams）和导演迈克尔·格雷西（Michael Gracey）的香蕉，CGI猴子，以传记片“更好的男人”为特色：“它正在治愈”</a></strong></li></ul><p>威廉姆斯目前以英国第一张专辑最多的独奏艺术家持有唱片。现在，以他的第15位纪录，他与甲壳虫乐队的纪录处于同一范围。</p><p> “ Rock DJ”在他的独奏作品中总共拥有20张排行榜的英国专辑，以及他作为90年代流行乐队的一部分的作品<a href="/artists/Take-That">。</a>英国排行榜的排行榜专辑将他排在了甲壳虫乐队的保罗·<a href="/artists/Paul-McCartney">麦卡尼（Paul McCartney</a> ）之后，他拥有一张很酷的英国专辑（甲壳虫乐队，<a href="/artists/Wings">翅膀</a>，独奏，以及他已故的妻子琳达·麦卡特尼（Linda McCartney））。</p><p>在谈到新闻稿中的成就时，威廉姆斯分享道：“感谢所有支持专辑和电影的人。获得我的第一张英国第一张专辑是多么巨大的荣誉。特别感谢我所有的粉丝，我从未理所当然的支持。我为这部电影<em>更好的男人</em>感到骄傲，所以让配乐专辑《触手可及的第一》使它变得更加特别。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DFN44UHukzy/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899